## Firebase Admin SDK Setup

This project uses Firebase Admin SDK to connect to Firestore from the backend.

To set this up:

1. Go to your [Firebase Console]
2. Navigate to **Project Settings > Service Accounts**
3. Click **"Generate new private key"** and download the `serviceAccountKey.json` file
4. Save the file to the project directory at: `./backend/serviceAccountKey.json`
5. Make sure to add `serviceAccountKey.json` to your `.gitignore` to avoid exposing sensitive credentials
